text-to-speech-http is a small web app for converting text into speech over HTTP

Requirements:
ruby
sinatra
lame - http://lame.sourceforge.net
espeak - http://espeak.sourceforge.net
portaudio - http://www.portaudio.com/ for building espeak

Install:
git clone https://github.com/ujjawal/text-to-speech-http.git
cd text-to-speech-http 
ruby lib/espeak-http

Use:
http://localhost:4567/tts?text=Hello%20world
